As part of the Legal Excellence and Risk team at Hall & Wilcox, I work with the firm's commercial groups to produce documents of the highest quality which are easy to work with and which meet our clients' legal and commercial needs.  With over 13 years' experience in Commercial and Property Law, my goal is to use the drafting skills and broad knowledge I have developed to provide the documents, information and advice our people need in order to deliver the best commercial outcomes for our clients. 

Hall & Wilcox is committed to practicing Smarter Law. For my part, this means:
- building strong relationships with my colleagues;
- contributing to a friendly culture where knowledge and ideas are freely shared;
- constantly learning and staying up to date with the law;
- identifying opportunities to use technology to provide the best service; 
- helping to implement the firm's innovative Smarter Law strategies.

